@startuml readme-llm-architecture-overview
'==============================================================================
' Diagram  : LLM Architecture Overview (README companion)
' Version  : v3
' Date     : 2026-06-17
' Audience : README / docs readers — the main request path, not every field.
' Type     : SIMPLIFIED MAINTAINED COMPANION of llm-spi-provider-architecture.puml.
'            One idea: a pluggable provider stack with centralised retry.
' Source   : agentforge4j-llm-api, agentforge4j-llm, provider modules (live)
'            + llm-spi-provider-architecture.puml.
'==============================================================================
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangleBorderThickness 1
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 36
skinparam ranksep 30
skinparam padding 4
hide empty members
top to bottom direction

rectangle "  Runtime / AgentInvoker  " as Runtime
rectangle "  LlmClient (interface)  " as Client
rectangle "  RetryingLlmClient  \n  (centralised retry)  " as Retry
rectangle "  Providers  \n  OpenAI / Claude / Bedrock  \n  + more  " as Providers
rectangle "  LlmClientFactory  \n  (+ ModelTierResolver)  \n  creates & selects the provider client  " as Factory

Runtime --> Client : calls execute()
Client  --> Retry  : resolved to
Retry   --> Providers : wraps provider client
Factory --> Providers : creates / selects

@enduml
